<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1917-09-17T07:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1917-09-17T07:00:00-05:00" n="446" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d446">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 763.72111Sp1/79</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">The Consul at Seville</hi> (<persName type="from"><hi rend="italic">Gracey</hi></persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the
                                    <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                            </hi>
                        </head>
                        <opener>
                            <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                        </opener>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Seville</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1917-09-17T12:00:00+00:00">
                                    <hi rend="italic">September 17, 1917, noon</hi></date>. <lb/>
                                    [<hi rend="italic">Received 11.55 p.m.</hi>]</dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>Consular agent, Cadiz, reports German submarine <hi rend="italic">U–293</hi> which entered Cadiz September 9, 7 a.m., will be
                            interned; wireless has been removed, munitions unloaded, officer on
                            parole, members are going to San Fernando; damage was broken propeller
                            shaft.</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <persName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Gracey</hi>
                                </persName>
                            </signed>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>